    "id": "nce1-083-084-going-on-holiday",
    "title": "Lesson 83: Going on holiday",
    "audioFilename": "083&084－Going on Holiday.mp3",
    "duration": 99.004,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.59,
      "end": 4.99,
      "text": "Lesson 83–Going on Holiday.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第83课——度假。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 6.81,
      "end": 10.69,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 12.37,
      "end": 16.25,
      "text": "Where did Sam go for his holiday this year?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "萨姆今年去哪里度假了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 18.98,
      "end": 19.94,
      "text": "Hello, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 20.64,
      "end": 21.28,
      "text": "Come in.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "进来吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 23.12,
      "end": 23.98,
      "text": "Hi, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 24.68,
      "end": 25.9,
      "text": "We're having lunch.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们正在吃午饭。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 26.9,
      "end": 29.72,
      "text": "Do you want to have lunch with us?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你想和我们一起吃午饭吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 30.64,
      "end": 32.64,
      "text": "No, thank you, Tom.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不了，谢谢，汤姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 33.26,
      "end": 35.1,
      "text": "I've already had lunch.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我已经吃过午饭了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 35.96,
      "end": 38.94,
      "text": "I had lunch at half past twelve.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我十二点半吃的午饭。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 40.02,
      "end": 42.14,
      "text": "Have a cup of coffee, then?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那喝杯咖啡吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 42.86,
      "end": 45.68,
      "text": "I've just had a cup, thank you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我刚喝过一杯，谢谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 46.2,
      "end": 48.54,
      "text": "I had one after my lunch.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "午饭后喝的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 49.92,
      "end": 52.74,
      "text": "Let's go into the living room, Carol.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们去客厅吧，卡罗尔。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 53.64,
      "end": 55.98,
      "text": "We can have our coffee there.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们可以在那里喝咖啡。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 57.12,
      "end": 62.62,
      "text": "Excuse the mess. This room's very untidy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "屋里很乱，请别介意。这房间太不整洁了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 63.48,
      "end": 65.52,
      "text": "We're packing our suitcases.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们正在收拾行李箱。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 66.6,
      "end": 68.72,
      "text": "We're going to leave tomorrow.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们明天就要出发。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 69.96,
      "end": 73.14,
      "text": "Tom and I are going to have a holiday.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "汤姆和我要去度假。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 74.38,
      "end": 75.64,
      "text": "Aren't you lucky?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你们真幸运，不是吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 77.48,
      "end": 80.78,
      "text": "When are you going to have a holiday, Sam?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "萨姆，你准备什么时候去度假？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 80.78,
      "end": 82.8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我不知道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 83.44,
      "end": 86.82,
      "text": "I've already had my holiday this year.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我今年已经度过假了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 88.06,
      "end": 89.46,
      "text": "Where did you go?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你去了哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s026",
      "start": 90.18,
      "end": 91.68,
      "text": "I stayed at home.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我待在家里。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
